dataset_id: High Mountain Asia LIS Model Terrestrial Hydrological Parameters V001
title: High Mountain Asia LIS Model Terrestrial Hydrological Parameters V001
summary: The data provided in this data set are simulated using the Noah-Multiparameterization Land Surface Model (Noah-MP LSM) Version 3.6 within the NASA Land Information System (LIS) Version 7.2. The data files contain estimates of water, energy fluxes, and land surface states for the High Mountain Asia (HMA) region.
